9) Putting It All Together
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
• Run npm run dev in the root folder of your Next.js app.  
• Ensure your wallet is on the correct network (e.g., Sepolia if you deployed there).  
• Navigate to /mint (if you’re an admin with MINTER_ROLE), fill in the fields, and click Mint.  
• After minting, you can navigate to /marketplace to list a newly minted token.  
• Make sure your user has approved the marketplace contract for that token (in real usage, approval is done via the ERC721 contract or via a separate approve step).  

